Zanzibar Blu — Multi-Agent AI Reservation System

Multi-agent AI platform automating hospitality reservations and customer support operations. Integrates natural language understanding, dynamic availability logic, and backend booking workflows.

What It Does
Zanzibar Blu replaces manual front-desk reservation handling with a 24/7 AI system that takes bookings, answers guest questions, checks availability, and manages the full reservation lifecycle — without human intervention.
